    <item>
      <title>印度将于五月前用文职人员取代驻马尔代夫的军队</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india-replace-troops-maldives-with-civilians-by-may-2024-02-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马尔代夫外交部周六表示，印度将在五月前从马尔代夫撤军，两国正在寻求就撤军达成协议，这导致两国关系紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/india-replace-troops-maldives-with-civilians-by-may-2024-02-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 11:40:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国因批评尹总统言论而召见俄罗斯特使</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-summons-russian-envoy-over-criticism-president-yoons-remarks-foreign-2024-02-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国外交部周六召见俄罗斯驻首尔特使，就莫斯科批评韩国总统尹锡烈最近关于朝鲜寻求核武库的言论提出投诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-summons-russian-envoy-over-criticism-president-yoons-remarks-foreign-2024-02-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 11:20:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国与斯里兰卡签署自由贸易协定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-sri-lanka-sign-free-trade-agreement-2024-02-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国和斯里兰卡周六签署了自由贸易协定，斯里兰卡希望此举将帮助其摆脱数十年来最严重的金融危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-sri-lanka-sign-free-trade-agreement-2024-02-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 10:57:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦前总理伊姆兰·汗和妻子因非法婚姻被判入狱7年</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-ex-pm-imran-khan-wife-get-7-years-unlawful-marriage-ary-news-2024-02-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦前总理伊姆兰·汗 (Imran Khan) 和他的妻子布什拉·汗 (Bushra Khan) 周六被一家法院判处七年监禁并罚款，该党裁定他们 2018 年的婚姻违法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-ex-pm-imran-khan-wife-get-7-years-unlawful-marriage-ary-news-2024-02-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 10:55:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼央行：应有降息空间，等待卢比走强</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesia-cbank-should-be-room-cut-rates-awaiting-stronger-rupiah-2024-02-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼央行行长佩里·沃吉约(Perry Warjiyo)周六表示，印尼央行今年有降息空间以提振经济增长，但正在等待卢比兑美元走强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesia-cbank-should-be-room-cut-rates-awaiting-stronger-rupiah-2024-02-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 09:45:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜睫毛如何以“中国制造”的身份进入西方</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/how-north-korean-eyelashes-make-their-way-west-made-china-2024-02-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜假睫毛的销售额达数百万美元——在世界各地的美容店以“中国制造”的名义销售——去年帮助推动了这个神秘国家的出口复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/how-north-korean-eyelashes-make-their-way-west-made-china-2024-02-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 07:02:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国称菲律宾船只“非法”登陆有争议的环礁</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-vessel-illegally-landed-disputed-atoll-2024-02-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国周六表示，一艘来自菲律宾的小型民用船只“非法停泊在两国声称拥有主权的南海环礁的海滩上”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-vessel-illegally-landed-disputed-atoll-2024-02-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 06:29:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜于2月2日试射巡航导弹-朝中社</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-tested-firing-cruise-missiles-feb-2-kcna-2024-02-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官方媒体周六报道称，朝鲜于 2 月 2 日在西海岸试射了巡航导弹和新型陆对空导弹，证实了一系列旨在增强防御能力的武器发射。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-tested-firing-cruise-missiles-feb-2-kcna-2024-02-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 21:59:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>恒大电动汽车暂停与迪拜 NWTN 就重新起草协议进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/evergrande-ev-unit-suspends-talks-with-dubais-nwtn-redrafting-deal-2024-02-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国恒大新能源汽车 (NEV) 周五表示，已暂停与迪拜出行公司 NWTN 签订的价值 38.9 亿港元（合 4.9742 亿美元）的股份认购协议条款的修订谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/evergrande-ev-unit-suspends-talks-with-dubais-nwtn-redrafting-deal-2024-02-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 15:49:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰扩大与斯洛伐克的边境管制以阻止非法移民</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/poland-extends-border-controls-with-slovakia-stem-illegal-migration-2024-02-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰内政部周五表示，波兰已将与斯洛伐克的边境管制延长至 3 月 2 日，以阻止非法移民从斯洛伐克领土进入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/poland-extends-border-controls-with-slovakia-stem-illegal-migration-2024-02-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 15:43:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
